<!-- PB:B: heading --><h3 class="h4 m4" id="h2--tedbooks">TEDBooks
</h3>

<!-- PB:B: image --><div class='pages-image'>
<img alt='' class='pages-image__content' src='//pb-assets.tedcdn.com/system/baubles/files/000/002/291/original/OTP_TEDBooks_covers_layout.png?1425586410'>
</div>


<!-- PB:B: copy --><div class='copy text-left'>
<p>OTP volunteers played a pivotal role in the release of TEDBooks talks by <a href="http://www.ted.com/talks/zak_ebrahim_i_am_the_son_of_a_terrorist_here_s_how_i_chose_peace">Zak Ebrahim</a> and <a href="http://www.ted.com/talks/pico_iyer_the_art_of_stillness">Pico Iyer</a>, translating them into 20 languages before posting. As a result, international partners co-premiered and promoted the talks. Zak Ebrahim’s talk was the fastest-spreading talk of all time, reaching 1.6 million views in one week.</p>

</div>



